And - Dear User - I've hidden some easter eggs. Come on, find them ;)


Usage: fubar [-i|--instant] [-q|--quiet] [[-t|--term] TERM]
       fubar --safe [[-t|--term] TERM]
       fubar --about TOPIC
       
  -i --instant        Do not load my ~/.config/fubar/autoload
  -q --quiet          Be quiet.
  -t --term TERM      Calculate the given term.
     --safe           Safe-mode, does not read or modify any file.
     --help           Help screen.
     --about TOPIC    Help about a specific topic.
     
--term implies -q
--safe implies -qi
